title.narrative: Provision of expertise (secondments) to the European Union (2015 to 2020)

description.narrative: This activity (Provision of expertise (secondments) to the European Union (2015 to 2020)) is a component of Enhancing the capacity of the European Union through the provision of expertise reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Multilateral organisation' and a budget of £11,973,876. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Sectors not specified. , with the following implementing partners: Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office. The start date is 01-07-2015 and the end date is 31-03-2020.
